OL,3,CAdvisers issue stark warning UK is
OL,4,Cunprepared for coming climate
OL,5,C'disaster'
OL,7,FThe Government is failing to prepare
OL,8,Fthe UK for "tomorrow's disaster" of
OL,9,Ffloods, heatwaves, drought and
OL,10,Fwildfires, its climate advisers have
OL,11,Fwarned.
OL,13,FThe independent advisory Climate
OL,14,FChange Committee also raised fears
OL,15,Fspending needed to protect communities
OL,16,Fand critical services such as the NHS
OL,17,Ffrom worsening weather extremes could
OL,18,Fbe cut in the summer spending review.
