OL,4,Cunprepared for coming climate
OL,5,C'disaster'
OL,7,FIn a new report on adaptation `
OL,8,Fhelping the UK cope with the already
OL,9,Finevitable impacts of climate change `
OL,10,Fthe committee warned there had been no
OL,11,Fimprovement since its last assessment
OL,12,Fin 2023, and accused the new
OL,13,Fgovernment of failing to deliver the
OL,14,Fchange in approach needed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
