OL,3,CAdvisers issue stark warning UK is
OL,4,Cunprepared for coming climate
OL,5,C'disaster'
OL,7,FThe report warns 6.3 million homes and
OL,8,Fproperties in England are currently at
OL,9,Frisk of flooding, which is set to rise
OL,10,Fto eight million ` one in four ` by
OL,11,F2050, while early deaths from
OL,12,Fheatwaves are projected to rise from
OL,13,Fthe 3,000 seen in 2022's record hot
OL,14,Fsummer to 10,000 a year by mid-century.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/19
