OL,3,CAdvisers issue stark warning UK is
OL,4,Cunprepared for coming climate
OL,5,C'disaster'
OL,7,FWithout action on climate change, the
OL,8,FUK will suffer a 7% hit to its
OL,9,Feconomic output by 2050, while rising
OL,10,Fsea levels are worsening coastal
OL,11,Fflooding and extreme temperatures and
OL,12,Fdrought drive an increased number of
OL,13,Fwildfires.
OL,15,FAlready, half the UK's prime
OL,16,Fagricultural farmland is at risk of
OL,17,Fflooding, which is set to worsen,
OL,18,Fwhile schools, hospitals and care
OL,19,Fhomes are among the most vulnerable to
OL,20,Fimpacts such as heatwaves, the
OL,21,Fcommittee warned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
