OL,3,CAdvisers issue stark warning UK is
OL,4,Cunprepared for coming climate
OL,5,C'disaster'
OL,7,FThe committee's chairwoman Baroness
OL,8,FBrown pointed to 2022's heatwave, when
OL,9,Ftemperatures topped 40C for the first
OL,10,Ftime ever, which in addition to
OL,11,Fthousands of deaths put huge pressure
OL,12,Fon emergency services and halted
OL,13,Foperations in hospitals.
OL,15,FAnd she warned children were sitting
OL,16,Fnational examinations that define
OL,17,Ftheir future in summer in sweltering
OL,18,Ftemperatures, while record wet
OL,19,Fconditions from 2022-2024 caused
OL,20,Fdevastating flooding and damage to
OL,21,Ffood production.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
