OL,4,Cunprepared for coming climate
OL,5,C'disaster'
OL,7,F"All of this and we are seeing no
OL,8,Fincrease in action," Baroness Brown
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FThe committee's assessment looked at
OL,12,F46 areas where adaptation needed to be
OL,13,Fdelivered, and found only good
OL,14,Fprogress in plans and policies for
OL,15,Fthree ` making rail and strategic road
OL,16,Fnetworks reliable and ensuring risks
OL,17,Fwere properly disclosed and managed by
OL,18,Ffinancial institutions.
