OL,5,C'disaster'
OL,7,FOn delivery, not a single measure `
OL,8,Ffrom ensuring resilience in nature and
OL,9,Ffarmland to water, food and energy
OL,10,Fsupplies ` was making good progress,
OL,11,Fwith 12 areas rated insufficient.
OL,13,FThe committee warned delivery had
OL,14,Factually worsened in the water sector
OL,15,Fbecause of a lack of credible plans to
OL,16,Fcut leaks and reduce water demand in
OL,17,Fthe face of worsening drought risk.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
