OL,7,FThe committee said the previous
OL,8,Fgovernment's action plan fell short of
OL,9,Fpreparing the UK for the climate
OL,10,Fchange already being experienced, let
OL,11,Falone the future, but found little
OL,12,Fevidence of change now despite
OL,13,FLabour's manifesto promising to
OL,14,F"improve resilience and preparation"
OL,15,Ffor the country.
