OL,7,FBaroness Brown said: "People are
OL,8,Fworrying about the impacts of extreme
OL,9,Fweather, worrying about food prices.
OL,10,FPeople are worried about what's going
OL,11,Fto happen to their vulnerable friends
OL,12,Fand relatives.
OL,14,F"Despite all this, we are seeing no
OL,15,Fsuch change in activity from the new
OL,16,Fgovernment, despite the fact that it's
OL,17,Fclear to my committee, it's
OL,18,Fincreasingly clear to the public that
OL,19,Fthe current approach to adaptation
OL,20,Fpolicy just isn't working.
