OL,7,FStandards for new homes need to
OL,8,Fprevent overheating and ensure they
OL,9,Fare not at risk of flooding, while
OL,10,Fagricultural subsidies, the 25-year
OL,11,Ffarming plan and food strategy should
OL,12,Fall support efforts to adapt nature
OL,13,Fand food production to the changing
OL,14,Fclimate.
OL,16,FBaroness Brown also suggested the
OL,17,Flevel of personal protective equipment
OL,18,F(PPE) still being used post-Covid
OL,19,Fneeded to be reviewed, to reduce costs
OL,20,Fand plastic waste and allow staff to
OL,21,Fwork more comfortably in the heat.
