OL,8,Fimprove its objectives and set clear
OL,9,Ftargets for what needs to be achieved,
OL,10,Fimprove coordination across
OL,11,Fdepartments, and implement monitoring
OL,12,Fand evaluation of climate impacts and
OL,13,Fthe effect of adaptation measures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
