OL,7,FThis summer's spending review must
OL,8,Fensure climate adaptation planning is
OL,9,Fsupported with sufficient resources,
OL,10,Fcritical public services such as the
OL,11,FNHS need to be resilient to current
OL,12,Fand future weather, and new
OL,13,Finfrastructure must be built with
OL,14,Fclimate in mind so it does not need
OL,15,Fcostly retrofitting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
