OL,7,FBut the committee raised concerns that
OL,8,Fthe Government had said last autumn
OL,9,Fthat there was a need to review flood
OL,10,Fdefence spending in light of financial
OL,11,Fpressures, raising fears it signalled
OL,12,Fcuts in the spending review.
OL,14,FBaroness Brown said: "We are seriously
OL,15,Fconcerned that resilience and climate
OL,16,Fadaptation may be cut in the spending
OL,17,Freview.
OL,19,F"Government needs to recognise this is
OL,20,Fnot a future problem, it's today's
OL,21,Fproblem," she urged.
