OL,8,F"wake-up call" for Government, with
OL,9,FWWF's head of climate policy Bella
OL,10,FO'Dowd saying: "The evidence is clear:
OL,11,Faction on climate unlocks economic
OL,12,Fopportunities, improves our health and
OL,13,Fsaves lives.
OL,15,F"Farmers, communities and businesses
