OL,7,FAnd Dr Friederike Otto, from Imperial
OL,8,FCollege London, an expert on climate's
OL,9,Frole in extreme weather said: "Climate
OL,10,Fchange is already hurting the UK `
OL,11,Fmore intense heatwaves and floods are
OL,12,Fdamaging infrastructure, reducing
OL,13,Fworker productivity, wiping out crops,
OL,14,Fand putting more pressure on the NHS.
OL,16,F"Given the Government's current focus
OL,17,Fon growth, it is hard to believe there
OL,18,Fhas not been a renewed focus on
OL,19,Fadaptation, which could save the UK
OL,20,Fbillions of pounds in avoided losses."
